law.history: Repealed 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 198, sec. 19, effective October 1, 1996. -- Created 1991 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 15, sec. 11, effective July 1, 1991.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Judicial review of pretrial license suspension for person under twenty-one.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/96). Under 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 198, sec. 20, the repeal of this statute by Section 19 of that Act becomes effective October 1, 1996.
